{"tid":1913943,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺最近黑警瘋狂抄牌 其實係借抄牌之名","createTime":"2020-03-07T07:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T18:16:03.000Z","uid":181549,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8952a85555452ee40abe18228b1503acb83d5438","tid":1913943,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T07:40:10.000Z","msg":"大家有無發覺黑警最近瘋狂抄牌<br />\n一架車落地搵幾隻藍衫輔警求其揀幾架車黎抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係做野就抄哂成條街<br />\n先前就醫護罷工 係PWH出面條長龍側邊抄幾架<br />\n早兩日就厚福街趕車走 企係度等啲錶位一過鐘就抄<br />\n唔會留手<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得就係唔敢行咇<br />\n落車抄幾架就走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>借抄牌之名<br />\n以__為實</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n可以係為左睇下黃店幾撚多人排<br />\n又唔夠膽郁手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"b28226eadb8599cc7ae95a76f25ccf17da5e1de2","tid":1913943,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7711d6e2476ccb1e6d90b9874b67b1a77ac49418","tid":1913943,"uid":165749,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:01:15.000Z","msg":"一早全部轉哂做便衣行咇啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：方便揀野做"},{"pid":"dcbba70484e9c0678f3548f6892525c9403a92e6","tid":1913943,"uid":121867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:23:24.000Z","msg":"今日俾人抄咗兩張 分別係10am同1pm<br />\n使唔使密到咁"},{"pid":"ead3da6107c786c94fd640baafb7435f7c5b0c87","tid":1913943,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcbba70484e9c0678f3548f6892525c9403a92e6","tid":1913943,"uid":121867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:23:24.000Z","msg":"今日俾人抄咗兩張 分別係10am同1pm<br />\n使唔使密到咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:24:41.000Z","msg":"係瘋狂抄 見到唔留手係咁抄 食屎狗"},{"pid":"fc581ab23d684c160d836304a9703457a47c8750","tid":1913943,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":